{"questionId":"9077051","questionHtml":"<p>State the unit of <em>c</em>.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{m^{\\frac{3}{2}}}\">\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mi>m</mi>\n      <mrow>\n        <mfrac>\n          <mn>3</mn>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n        </mfrac>\n      </mrow>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>&nbsp;✔</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em>Accept other power of tens multiples of&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{m^{\\frac{3}{2}}}\">\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mi>m</mi>\n      <mrow>\n        <mfrac>\n          <mn>3</mn>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n        </mfrac>\n      </mrow>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>, eg:&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{cm^{\\frac{3}{2}}}\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mi>c</mi>\n    <msup>\n      <mi>m</mi>\n      <mrow>\n        <mfrac>\n          <mn>3</mn>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n        </mfrac>\n      </mrow>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>.</em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"9077051","referenceCode":"18N.3.SL.TZ0.a","subjectId":"46-dp-physics-last-assessment-2024","title":"State the unit of c.","paper":"3","level":"SL","questionNumber":"a","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 1]","breadcrumbLabels":["Core","Core","Topic 1: Measurements and uncertainties","1.2 – Uncertainties and errors","Core","Topic 1: Measurements and uncertainties"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}}}